    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to national and international voluntary groups and organizations, unaffiliated with any government and usually nonprofit, such as the UN (from which body the term originated), charity groups, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
